name: Mixed Urgency Keywords
description: Contains both high and medium urgency keywords
transcript: Hi, I'm Lisa Martinez. I was evicted from my apartment two weeks ago and I'm currently staying in a temporary shelter. The situation is urgent because I have two young children and we can't stay at the shelter much longer. I need help with finding new housing and getting the money together for a deposit. I'm looking for about two thousand dollars. I'm in Phoenix, Arizona. Please help us.

segments.text: I was evicted from my apartment two weeks ago and I'm currently staying in a temporary shelter.
